<problem id="fs-idp44505440">
<para id="fs-idp17610848">A secondary plant compound might be used for which of the following?</para>
<list id="fs-idp87686192" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>a new crop variety</item>
<item>a new drug</item>
<item>a soil nutrient</item>
